        <abstract>
            <p>Sends a number of questions (to put to his father), mainly concerned with transmission of diseases, between Europeans and natives, "people packed together", etc.</p> 
<p>Is investigating how to get Government support [for <hi rend="italic">Zoology</hi>].</p> 
